verbose_text: The mean urinary MDA : Cr ratios at birth (2.62 +/- 0.29 mug/mg) and after 48 hr (3.70 +/- 52 mug/mg) were elevated significantly in newborns with perinatal asphyxia compared to the controls (1.63 +/- 0.19 mug/mg vs. 1.96 +/- 0.15; P < 0.001).
